According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Large Size TFT-LCD Market was valued at USD 18.34 billion in 2025 and is projected to reach USD 23.82 billion by 2034, expanding at a CAGR of 3.8% during the forecast period. The market continues to grow steadily due to increasing demand for large-format display panels across televisions, gaming monitors, notebooks, digital signage, and automotive cockpit displays. Ongoing advancements in TFT-LCD technology, including Mini-LED backlighting, higher refresh rates, improved color accuracy, and energy-efficient panel designs, are enabling manufacturers to remain competitive despite increasing competition from OLED and Micro-LED technologies.
